{
  "stem": "12684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they're-- why don't you get it yourself?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a very wrong thing to say because there was a small restaurant by the lake, and I went in there and I said, I would like to have an ice cream.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, oh, how nice to see you again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your friends are in the big restaurant across the lake.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, oh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's a boat going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Would you like to go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not sooner said but done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the consequences were that I was lost and they didn't know where I was and they questioned these people and they had to send somebody else to get me out of this other restaurant, where an awful lot of my friends were.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I was called to the Gestapo headquarters and I got quite a calling down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not to ever do it again or else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's the else?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he just told me that-- Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gertze, that I was not to do it again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I should promise him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I promised him not to go into that little restaurant ever again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know I should not go to any restaurant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Can I go home now?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they took me out of some friends' houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this was not a public place and they all said, tsk, tsk, tsk, tsk, now come on home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's soon curfew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they were, again, had to give account of what I did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, so I tried what I could just to have fun with these people, which amused me because I figured how dare these people to do that to me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one shift was from 10:00, no, from 6:00 to afternoon, I don't know, 2:00 or 3:00.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
